snippet.title: Emilia Responds To Replacing Amber Heard in Aquaman 2!
snippet.description:
Emilia Responds To Replacing Amber Heard in Aquaman 2
Fans of Johnny Depp have started a change.org petition to get Amber Heard out of Mara, and the number of individuals who have signed it has been growing in recent weeks. Unfortunately, as a result of the events that transpired in 2020, many things have been reorganised. What I mean is that a number of comic book movies that were supposed to be released were unable to do so, but things are starting to look up. This may not be the case in 2021, since comic book films, like other films, are expected to resume their regular release schedules.

💗 Hope you liked the video and would consider leaving a like and telling us what you thought in the comments!
